latestIgtvVideos.title: Drop sets
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Drop sets increase muscle size and endurance. By continuing an exercise at higher weights to lower weights,
you force your muscles to work as hard as they possibly can, 
like you do in competition. 
Although your arms and legs might get shiver after drop sets,

according to bodybuilder and trainer @TomVenuto. And @tomplatz 
Drop sets are designed for bodybuilders, They aren't particularly beneficial for building strength, power and speed, rather they are a useful tool for building muscle mass.

You need a really good spotters like @mananpatel95588 and @isnehpatel  to complete this kind of sets 
So this the answer for people who just started training and influence for drop sets and supers sets
